creator: Urban Technologies Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Urban makes renting easy, honest and empowering by bringing the entire rental journey online.
Browse, discover and rent inspected homes in Dubai, visit on your own through our secure digital locks, make an offer and choose a flexible payment option that works for you.
After you move in, get in touch with Urban support for all your maintenance questions.
Virtual tours for every home
• Discover spaces like never before with virtual tours
• Professional photography
Homes you can rely on.
• All the homes we list undergo a 150-point inspection report by a third party. No surprises
• We take quality seriously. All our properties are inspected and selected to give you the best living experience
Visit homes on your own.
• Visit apartments and villas on your own. All you need is your phone to unlock–book a slot and go
• Plenty of time to explore without anyone breathing down your neck
You make the offer.
• Set a fair price and outbid other renters for your new home.
• Whatever the offer, you’ll hear back by tomorrow.
Pay your rent monthly.
• Pay rent with your choice of payment plan, including monthly installments with our friends at Emirates NBD
• Skip the checks and pay by card to earn points
Support even after you’ve settled in
• WhatsApp chat, email or phone GoUrban support for all your questions
Browse, discover and rent inspected homes in Dubai. Choose from all kinds of homes:
- Apartments for rent
- Villas for rent
- Condos for rent
- Duplexes/Triplexes for rent
- Lofts for rent
- Townhouses for rent
- Rooms for rent
descriptionShort: Discover inspected homes to rent, visit on your own, make an offer & pay online

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:

• Introducing new homes without service fees

• You’ll now get an inspection report when visiting a home
• You can now make an offer when applying for the payment installments option
• Overall enhancements across the board. And as always, we asked some bugs to move out.

title: Urban: Real Estate & Home Rentals

creator: Urban Technologies Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Urban makes renting easy, honest and empowering by bringing the entire rental journey online.
Browse, discover and rent inspected homes in Dubai, visit on your own through our secure digital locks, make an offer and choose a flexible payment option that works for you.
After you move in, get in touch with Urban support for all your maintenance questions.
Virtual tours for every home
• Discover spaces like never before with virtual tours
• Professional photography
Homes you can rely on.
• All the homes we list undergo a 150-point inspection report by a third party. No surprises
• We take quality seriously. All our properties are inspected and selected to give you the best living experience
Visit homes on your own.
• Visit apartments and villas on your own. All you need is your phone to unlock–book a slot and go
• Plenty of time to explore without anyone breathing down your neck
You make the offer.
• Set a fair price and outbid other renters for your new home.
• Whatever the offer, you’ll hear back by tomorrow.
Pay your rent monthly.
• Pay rent with your choice of payment plan, including monthly installments with our friends at Emirates NBD
• Skip the checks and pay by card to earn points
Support even after you’ve settled in
• WhatsApp chat, email or phone GoUrban support for all your questions
Browse, discover and rent inspected homes in Dubai. Choose from all kinds of homes:
- Apartments for rent
- Villas for rent
- Condos for rent
- Duplexes/Triplexes for rent
- Lofts for rent
- Townhouses for rent
- Rooms for rent
